def get_permit_per_continent(filename, continents, permits):
    data = pd.read_csv(filename, delimiter=",")
    data = data[data["COMESFROMCOUNTRYID"] != "Not Applicable"]
    grouped_data = data.groupby(['NATIONALITYCONTINENT','RESIDENTPERMIT']).count()['DATEOFBIRTH']
    
    f_df = pd.DataFrame(index=continents, columns=permits)
    f_df = f_df.fillna(0)
    
    prev_continent = -1000
    #val = f_df.loc[9]

    for i in range(len(grouped_data)):
        c = list(grouped_data.index)[i][0]
        p = list(grouped_data.index)[i][1]
        v = list(grouped_data)[i]

        if prev_continent != c:
            if prev_continent != -1000:
                f_df.loc[prev_continent] = list(val)
                val["Total"] = sum(list(val))
            prev_continent = c
            val = f_df.loc[c]
            val[p] = v
        else:
            val[p] = v
    
    return f_df

In [33]:
def get_counries_for_continent(continent):
    countries = []
    for f in files:
        all_data = pd.read_csv(f, delimiter=",")
        filtered_data = all_data[all_data["NATIONALITYCONTINENT"] == continent]["NATIONALITYSTATE"].drop_duplicates()
        countries = list(set(countries + list(filtered_data)))
    return countries
In [34]:
def get_permit_per_country_for_continent(filename, permits, continent, countries):
    data = pd.read_csv(filename, delimiter=",")
    data = data[data["COMESFROMCOUNTRYID"] != "Not Applicable"]
    data = data[data["NATIONALITYCONTINENT"] == continent]
    grouped_data = data.groupby(['NATIONALITYSTATE','RESIDENTPERMIT']).count()['DATEOFBIRTH']
    
    countries = list(pd.read_csv(files[0], delimiter=",")['NATIONALITYSTATE'].drop_duplicates())
    countries.sort()
    
    f_df = pd.DataFrame(index=countries, columns=permits)
    f_df = f_df.fillna(0)
    
    prev_country = -1000
    #val = f_df.loc[9]

    for i in range(len(grouped_data)):
        c = list(grouped_data.index)[i][0]
        p = list(grouped_data.index)[i][1]
        v = list(grouped_data)[i]

        if prev_country != c:
            if prev_country != -1000:
                f_df.loc[prev_country] = list(val)
                val["Total"] = sum(list(val))
            prev_country = c
            if c in f_df.index:
                val = f_df.loc[c]
            else:
                val = pd.Series(np.zeros(len(permits)), index=permits)
            val[p] = v
        else:
            val[p] = v
    
    return f_df[(f_df.T != 0).any()]
